5. Data Security

We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your data against unauthorized access, loss, or misuse.

6. Data Retention

We retain your data only as long as necessary to provide services or comply with legal obligations.

7. Your Rights

You have the right to:

Access your data

Request correction or deletion

